headline: Gracie Terzian,  Jeffrey Emanuel
abstract: He rattled off sonnets by Shakespeare on their first date. She was impressed.
lead_paragraph: Grace Benedict Paine Terzian and Jeffrey Howard Emanuel were married Jan. 11 at UVA Inn at Darden in Charlottesville, Va. William N. Marshall Sr., the chief deputy sheriff in Charlottesville, officiated with George C. Paine II, an uncle of the bride, leading the ceremony.
